(363, 17, '_single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_2_short_headline', 'field_5de87be8452f9'),
(364, 17, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_2_description', 'Start your first full day in Vietnam with a wander around Hanoi’s beguiling Old Quarter. Navigate the hustle of narrow streets, packed with family-run cafés and stores selling everything from artwork to books and hand-embroidered Ao Dais.\r\n\r\nThe rest of the afternoon is yours to spend at leisure. As evening falls, head out for a rice wine tasting with local ceramic artists, with the bars of Hanoi at your disposal.'),
