(734, 144, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_1_description', 'You will be met at the airport and transferred to the hotel by taxi. This isn’t just any taxi, however, this is a taxi service especially for women and operated by women, created for resource-poor women in India to empower them with knowledge and skills so that they can earn a livelihood with dignity.\r\nTo help you relax after a long journey, we will bring a henna (known as mehndi in India) artist to you at our clean, modern hotel in South Delhi. Dinner will be provided tonight for those who have arrived in time.\r\nMEALS INCLUDED: Dinner'),
