(985, 147, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_2_description', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Following breakfast and your official tour orientation, we’ll be off to visit one of the most famous beaches here on Bali, Water Blow Beach, that has to be seen to be believed. From there we’ll visit the first of Bali’s best-kept secrets, Gunung Payung Beach before we head to the incredible Uluwatu Temple. Our day will end with a traditional welcome meal at a popular local restaurant.</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\r\n</span><b>MEALS INCLUDED:</b> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Breakfast, dinner</span>'),
