(998, 145, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_2_description', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This morning will be our first official group morning over a lovely breakfast at the hotel. We’ll have a short but detailed orientation to prepare you for India and her culture before we head out to explore this incredible city.</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">After visiting some of Delhi’s most beautiful sites, we will head to a local female-owned cooking school. Here you will learn about the Indian spices &amp; vegetables used to make the mouthwatering cuisine followed by a trip to the local market. Then we’ll become the chef’s with a private hands-on cooking lesson, followed by savouring the self-cooked 5-course meal!</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\r\n</span><b>MEALS INCLUDED:</b> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Breakfast, lunch, dinner</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\r\n</span>'),
