(1010, 135, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_2_description', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We’ll start this morning with an in-depth group orientation to discuss the tour in more detail, offer you ideas and advice on the culture and customs and ways to make the most of your time on this adventure.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We’ll then depart our hotel for an exciting and fascinating exploration of this amazing city, enjoy a traditional street food lunch and introduce you to the reasons why Bangkok is often named as ‘The Best City on the Planet’. This evening it’s more food as we dine at a lovely local restaurant after a fabulous first day.</span>\r\n\r\n<b>MEALS INCLUDED:</b> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Breakfast, lunch, dinner</span>'),
