(1022, 135, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_3_description', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Following breakfast, we’ll transfer to the airport for our quick flight north to the stunning city of Chiang Mai. Surrounded by mountains, Chiang Mai is the absolute opposite of Bangkok yet still maintains the irresistible Thai charm and hospitality.</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This evening we’ll venture out to the world-famous Chiang Mai night market for dinner and to wander the narrow rows of handmade crafts and stalls.</span>\r\n\r\n<b>MEALS INCLUDED:</b> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Breakfast, dinner</span>'),
