(1137, 144, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_3_headline', 'Old Delhi to Agra, India'),
(1138, 144, '_single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_3_headline', 'field_5de87c16452fe'),
(1139, 144, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_3_short_headline', 'India is all about the saree, so today we’ll show you how to wear your own'),
(1140, 144, '_single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_3_short_headline', 'field_5de87c16452ff'),
(1141, 144, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_3_description', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This morning we headed to the heart of the city - Old Delhi, where we’ll visit the world’s biggest wholesale spice market. The sounds, smells, and colors will make this an experience you’ll never forget! To really get with the local culture we’ll be traveling in a typical Indian style. That means auto-rickshaw, pedal rickshaw, and in the ‘women’s only’ carriage of the Delhi Metro (another of the ways that Delhi is working towards making this a woman-friendly city.)</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Now we’re ready to leave Delhi and head to Agra in our private coach that will stay with us for the remainder of the tour.</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">On arrival in Agra, we’ll check into our beautiful 4 star-hotel from where you can see the Taj Mahal from the rooftop pool! Once checked-in we’ll head to a local shop, where everyone can pick out their own complimentary saree; the traditional fashion for women in India. We will also include a saree tying class so you can wear it again and again.</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This evening is your free time to explore Agra’s many wonderful shops and cafes.</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\r\n</span><b>MEALS INCLUDED:</b> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Breakfast</span>'),
(1142, 144, '_single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_3_description', 'field_5de87c1645300'),
