(1199, 144, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_8_short_headline', 'You can’t visit India without trying Yoga, so today we have a special private class'),
(1200, 144, '_single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_8_short_headline', 'field_5de87cc961906'),
(1201, 144, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_8_description', 'We’ll start the day by experiencing a 2-hour yoga and meditation session, led by a ‘swami’ at a school registered by the Yoga Alliance. Even if you’ve never tried yoga before, you must join in like this a truly once-in-a-lifetime experience.\r\nLater on, you’ll have the opportunity to see myriad more reasons why Jaipur is so famous, including block printing, hand made rugs (that provide employment for many rural and underprivileged women) and shopping, shopping, shopping!\r\nAs Jaipur is the capital city of the Rajasthani province we will have a traditional Rajasthani dinner at one of the most popular restaurants in Jaipur, before settling in for the night at our comfortable, modern hotel.\r\nMEALS INCLUDED: Breakfast, dinner'),
