(1237, 144, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_11_description', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sadly this morning is where we say our official goodbyes with our last group breakfast. There will be ample time and opportunity for those final group photographs, swapping of contact details and arranging your future meet up’s. Your guide will be around for most of the day to help you with any onward travel plans, be they back to the airport or on to a new location. </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\r\n</span><b>MEALS INCLUDED:</b> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Breakfast</span>'),
