(1325, 142, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_6_short_headline', 'Dinner and a show at the world famous Cambodia Circus'),
(1326, 142, '_single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_6_short_headline', 'field_5de87cb1618fa'),
(1327, 142, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_6_description', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">By now you’ll have biked, trekked, upcycled and floated so today we’re giving you a day to recover! You’re free to lounge around the hotel pool or head out to the town for shopping or to visit the markets, bars, and restaurants. This evening we’ll be experiencing the unbelievable Cambodia Circus, famed for how it welcomes children from the slums and turns them into world-class performers; several of whom have since gone on to join the Cirque de Soleil performers on their world tours.</span>'),
