(1361, 142, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_9_short_headline', ' Take a ride on the world famous bamboo train!'),
(1362, 142, '_single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_9_short_headline', 'field_5de87cd36190c'),
(1363, 142, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_9_description', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We\'ve got a few activities lined up for you today but none will get you screaming with laughter as much as a ride on the bamboo train! Imagine hurtling along a train track on a bamboo platform atop train-like wheels! This is seriously good fun and it’s said that if you visit Cambodia without trying out this white-knuckled adventure, you haven’t really visited Cambodia. After this, we’ll take a slightly more sedate trip to a stunning cave in time for the nightly exodus of over a million bats out hunting for food.</span>'),
