(1399, 142, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_12_description', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sadly our tour is officially over today but before we separate there’ll be plenty of time for a final group photograph. If you need to return to Siem Reap our guides can help to arrange transport for you, or if you’d like us to pre-book a flight for you, just let our bookings team know in advance. Whatever your plan today your guide can help with any arrangements that you need.</span>'),
