(1447, 137, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_4_description', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This morning we’ll finish up any projects that need completing before lunch followed by a trumpet-like send-off before our transfer back to Chiang Mai city. Once back at our hotel, there’ll be plenty of time for a good shower and a freshen-up then it’s off to the world-famous night market for a traditional welcome dinner to officially celebrate the start of our tour together.</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\r\n</span><b>MEALS INCLUDED:</b> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Breakfast, lunch, dinner</span>'),
