(1495, 137, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_8_description', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">By now you’ll have earned yourself a little downtime so today you’re free to do as much or as little as you wish. Spend the day on the beach, around the pool, head to the shops and the markets, whatever you choose you can do this all under your own steam. Your guide will be able to assist you with any transport or activities that you may want to join and will be around all day to help with anything that you need.</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\r\n</span><b>MEALS INCLUDED:</b> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Breakfast</span>'),
