(1506, 137, '_single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_9_short_headline', 'field_5de87cd36190c'),
(1507, 137, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_9_description', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Koh Samui isn’t the only beautiful island in the Gulf of Thailand. It’s just one of several that are worthy of a Wild Ones tour. So today we’re departing Koh Samui and crossing by boat to Koh Tao, or Turtle Island. The crossing is almost as beautiful as the destination and is a wonderful opportunity to soak up the sun and relax.</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">On arrival on Turtle Island, it\'s a quick transfer to our next hotel where we’ll check-in before catching up around the pool, grabbing a cocktail and chatting through the plan for the next few days here.</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\r\n</span><b>MEALS INCLUDED:</b> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Breakfast</span>'),
