(1531, 137, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_11_description', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Koh Tao isn’t only about the water, however, it’s a lovely place to explore on land. Today you can do this under your own steam, or simply enjoy the beach, the pool, the bars and restaurants as today is your day to do as you please. There are plenty of activities to keep you active and your guide will be only too happy to help with arrangements.</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\r\n</span><b>MEALS INCLUDED:</b> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Breakfast</span>'),
