(1555, 137, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_13_description', 'Sadly, today we’ll be saying goodbye as we’ve reached the end of our adventure together. Your guide will be available to you for most of the day to assist with any onward journey plans that you may have. But before we separate there’ll be a chance for one last group photo, plenty of hugs and teary goodbyes.\r\n\r\nMEALS INCLUDED: Breakfast, dinner'),
