(1711, 136, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_3_short_headline', 'Day at the world’s largest outdoor market'),
(1712, 136, '_single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_3_short_headline', 'field_5de87c16452ff'),
(1713, 136, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_3_description', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you’ve ever spoken to anybody who’s been to Thailand, they’ll have no doubt told you of the excellent shopping and markets. Well, today we’ll be visiting the very best of those, and still the largest outdoor market on the planet. Known locally as the “JJ” market, this is a great location to shop, eat, drink and watch the world go by. If there’s anything that you want to buy here in Thailand, then this is absolutely the place to do it.</span>\r\n\r\n<b>MEALS INCLUDED:</b> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Breakfast</span>'),
