(1723, 136, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_4_short_headline', 'Flight to Koh Samui and transfer to beachside hotel'),
(1724, 136, '_single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_4_short_headline', 'field_5de87c2645305'),
(1725, 136, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_4_description', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sadly, today we have to say goodbye to Bangkok, but every cloud has a silver lining as we’re heading south to the most beautiful of Thailand’s islands, Koh Samui. Our flight will take us just over an hour and once we arrive at Samui airport, it’s a quick transfer to our hotel situated in the heart of Koh Samui, a town called Chaweng. Located right on the beach, with two swimming pools, this hotel has everything you need to really kickback and relax to make the most of your time here.</span>\r\n\r\n<b>MEALS INCLUDED:</b> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Breakfast, dinner</span>'),
