(1737, 136, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_5_description', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In addition to being told about shopping and markets, you have probably heard about the elephants in Thailand and perhaps the poor treatment they receive from some of the more unscrupulous operators. The welfare of elephants is something that is very close to our hearts here at Wild Ones and we actively support several animal welfare projects in Thailand. Today we’re going to take you to visit one such location so that you can see for yourself the excellent work being carried out by some organizations who have the welfare of these wonderful beasts </span><b>at heart.</b>\r\n\r\n<b>MEALS INCLUDED:</b> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Breakfast, lunch</span>'),
