(1749, 136, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_6_description', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">After a genuinely incredible day with the elephants yesterday, today we’ll be showing you more of the island on our excellent island safari tour. We’ll be seeking out the best beaches, viewpoints and showing you life away from tourism. We’ll return to the hotel in time for their legendary Wednesday night party!</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\r\n</span><b>MEALS INCLUDED:</b> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Breakfast, lunch</span>'),
