(1761, 136, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_7_description', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You lucky, lucky people! We’re not just treating you to one beautiful island, that would be a waste! So today we’re switching islands from Koh Samui to Phuket - Thailand’s number one tourist destination. We’ll catch a quick flight from Samui in the Gulf of Thailand to Phuket in the Andaman sea. On arrival, it’s a quick transfer to our new hotel in the town of Patong on the islands west coast. </span>\r\n\r\n<b>MEALS INCLUDED</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">:</span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Breakfast</span>'),
