(1773, 136, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_8_description', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">After a week of high energy activity we think you deserve a little break so today is yours to do as much or as little as you please. Spend the day relaxing by the pool, head down to the beach or out to explore the island under your own steam. Your guide will be around to help you with any activities you’d like to join and to ensure that you get the best available service. Take your time today as tomorrow we’re on another island adventure.</span>\r\n\r\n<b>MEALS INCLUDED:</b> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Breakfast</span>'),
