(1785, 136, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_9_description', '<b>DAY NINE</b> <b>- Phuket, Thailand</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Today we’ll be taking to the high seas for a beautiful boat trip around the surrounding islands. Crystal clear warm seas invite us to explore under the surface so grab your snorkel gear and jump in! We’ll visit a few islands today and for those who aren’t up for checking out the marine life, there’s no better place to top up your tan!</span>\r\n\r\n<b>MEALS INCLUDED:</b> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Breakfast,</span>'),
