(1809, 136, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_11_description', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hopefully the farewells this morning won’t be too teary! We’ll enjoy one last breakfast together to say our final farewells, swap contact details, have a final group photo and plenty of hugs all around. Your guide will be around to help you organize any onward travel that you may have and to make sure you’re leaving with only the very best of memories. </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\r\n</span><b>MEALS INCLUDED:</b> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Breakfast, dinner</span>'),
