(1857, 140, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_4_description', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To really be able to explore the sites and the ruins of Ayutthaya we need to do so by bicycle. Ayutthaya is as flat as a pancake and so there’s really no need to be a Tour de France champion to enjoy this day. We’ll be taking it very easy, but today you’ll learn so much about this ancient empire that will really benefit you as we travel on to other locations.</span>\r\n\r\n<b>MEALS INCLUDED:</b> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Breakfast, lunch, dinner</span>'),
