(1869, 140, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_5_description', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">After a hearty breakfast, it’s just a quick 60-minute transfer to Bangkok’s international airport for our flight north to the beautiful, ancient city of Chiang Mai. Steeped in history, surrounded by mountains with a wonderful, laid-back vibe, Chiang Mai is the perfect place to both relax and discover more about the history of this incredible part of the world.</span>\r\n\r\n<b>MEALS INCLUDED</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">:</span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Breakfast, lunch, dinner</span>'),
