(1953, 140, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_12_description', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It’s time to say our sad farewells today as our whirlwind tour is officially over. Your guide will still be around for the morning to help you with any onward travel that you may require or to help you get back to the airport. But before we head our separate ways there’ll be plenty of time for one final group photo, plenty of hugs and teary farewell hugs.</span>\r\n\r\n<b>MEALS INCLUDED:</b> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Breakfast</span>'),
