(1991, 135, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_5_description', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We’ll carry on our activities with the elephants and the staff here this morning, departing the sanctuary after lunch. There’ll be lots of time for your ‘elephant-selfies’ and to make sure you’ve had your fill of elephant hugs! Rest assured that the time we spend here is going along to ensuring a bright and healthy future for these majestic beasts and the communities that support them.</span>\r\n\r\n<b>MEALS INCLUDED:</b> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Breakfast, lunch, dinner</span>'),
