(2015, 135, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_7_description', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Chiang Mai will be difficult to leave, that for sure! But when you see where we’re heading too next it’ll make the flight to the island of Koh Samui much easier to take. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">On arrival on the island, we’ll take a quick transfer to the town of Chaweng on the islands east side. This is the main town on the island and is a great place to rest up and enjoy everything that you need to recover as you feel the soft golden sands between your toes.</span>\r\n\r\n<b>MEALS INCLUDED:</b> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Breakfast, dinner</span>'),
