(2027, 135, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_8_description', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Koh Samui is a real mixture of modern Thailand and traditional island living. Today we’re taking a tour to show you how the island has developed over the years and is one of the leading destinations of tourism in southeast Asia. We’ll explore the most areas of natural beauty and show you sights usually unseen by the average tourist.</span>\r\n\r\n<b>MEALS INCLUDED:</b> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Breakfast, lunch</span>'),
