(2039, 135, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_9_description', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Of course, being surrounded by warm, crystal clear water, it wouldn’t be a trip to this area without spending some time exploring the locale by boat. So today we’re off to explore an area of stunning natural beauty at Ang Thong Marine Park. There’ll be opportunity to swim and snorkel and alight the boat to explore these amazing islands on foot.</span>\r\n\r\n<b>MEALS INCLUDED:</b> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Breakfast, lunch, dinner</span>'),
