(2099, 139, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_2_description', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This morning begins with a group meeting to run through the plan for the day and the tour. Your guide will update you on anything that’s important to know so that you can just relax and enjoy your time with us.</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We’ll then head off to begin our tour of this buzzing and fascinating city and show you just why Bangkok is such a draw for tourists from all over the world. We’ll include a special meal for lunch at a popular street-side restaurant. </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This evening we’ll head out to a great little secret that we know, a very special vegetarian restaurant to celebrate our first full day on this unique and amazing tour.</span>\r\n\r\n<b>MEALS INCLUDED:</b> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Breakfast, lunch, dinner</span>'),
