(2147, 139, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_6_description', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">What we are sure is one of the days that you’re looking forward to the most, today we transfer to our sponsored elephant sanctuary located on the outskirts of the city. On arrival, we’ll be introduced to the team who dedicate their lives to ensuring safe and loving lives for these rescued elephants, and of course, we’ll also meet the elephants!</span>\r\n\r\n<b>MEALS INCLUDED:</b> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Breakfast, lunch, dinner</span>'),
