(2171, 139, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_8_description', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This morning we’ll continue any of our projects that we’ve not had the chance to complete. Then after lunch, it’s sadly time to leave. But not before we have one final group photo with our favorite elephants, and with a very fond farewell to the mahouts and the team who dedicate their lives to the ongoing care of these amazing animals. </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This afternoon you’ll have a chance to relax and think back to what an incredible experience you have just enjoyed. </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\r\n</span><b>MEALS INCLUDED:</b> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Breakfast, lunch, dinner</span>'),
