(2207, 139, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_11_description', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Today we return to where it all began, but not before there’s time to make sure we’ve all filled our cases with the local souvenirs. For coffee lovers amongst us, this is one of the best areas in southeast Asia to buy good quality beans in bulk. We’ll take a flight back south to Bangkok and then on to our stunning hotel located just a short trip from the airport. This is the perfect place to relax and unwind from what we promise will be an incredible tour from start to finish.</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This evening we’ll have our final group dinner and share a glass of wine or two; the perfect way to end the most unforgettable tour of a country that we know you’ll be eager to return to as soon as possible.</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\r\n</span><b>MEALS INCLUDED:</b> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Breakfast, dinner</span>'),
