(2279, 138, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_4_description', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The morning will begin with a relaxed breakfast and a chat to run through your time at the award-winning Absolute Sanctuary. It’s important to us that you’re properly prepared for your time here as your guide will leave you in the very capable hands of the Absolute experts. </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">On arrival at the sanctuary, we’ll have you checked in to your stunning rooms and introduced to the team so they can take you through your programs for the coming days.</span>\r\n\r\n<b>MEALS INCLUDED:</b> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Breakfast, dinner</span>'),
