(2291, 138, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_5_description', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Today will be your first full day of your program itinerary. Whichever program you choose to undertake our Guest Experience team will send you everything that you need to fully understand your program and to ensure that you’re fully prepared.With the correct preparation, your time at Absolute could easily be a life-changer, a step into a brand new you and one of the most incredible experiences of your life. </span>\r\n\r\n<b>MEALS INCLUDED:</b> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Breakfast, lunch, dinner</span>'),
