(2303, 138, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_6_description', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Your program will last five full days, include six nights of accommodation and all of your meals are prepared for you in the Sanctuaries incredible kitchen. Each day you will be taking part in several activities that are designed to maximise your time as a participant. You will be expertly led by the Absolute team of experts who have your health, well-being, and revitalisation as their key focus. Throughout your time at the sanctuary, should you wish to add any other activities to your program this can easily be organised through talking to the Absolute team.</span>\r\n\r\n<b>MEALS INCLUDED:</b> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Breakfast, lunch, dinner</span>'),
