(2818, 146, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_2_short_headline', 'Incredible private Hanoi city full day tour'),
(2819, 146, '_single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_2_short_headline', 'field_5de87be8452f9'),
(2820, 146, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_2_description', 'After breakfast and a formal orientation we’ll head off north west of Saigon to the Cu Chi tunnels. This fascinating tunnel complex was dug in 1948 but was made famous throughout the American/Vietnam war. Visit the underground villages to better understand the tunnels’ history, life in the tunnels and the Vietnamese’s resilience during the combats. We’ll also visit a few more incredible locations that will show you why this country is one of Asia’s fastest-growing tourist locations, such as the Reunification Palace, the charming Notre Dame Cathedral, the Old Post Office, the elegant Saigon Opera House and the bustling Ben Thanh Market.\r\nOvernight in Ho Chi Minh City.\r\nMEALS INCLUDED: Breakfast'),
