(2854, 146, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_5_short_headline', 'Sapa arrival with our private trip to a women\'s empowerment handicraft village'),
(2855, 146, '_single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_5_short_headline', 'field_5de87ca6618f4'),
(2856, 146, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_5_description', 'After breakfast, it’s a relaxing drive along the most beautiful coast of Vietnam to Hoi An. We’ll stop at the famous Hai Van pass for a panoramic view of white sand beach, blue sea and green mountains.\r\nArriving in Hoi An around noon there’s plenty of time to take a guided walking tour around Hoi An Ancient Town. Visit the Japanese Covered Bridge, Chinese Assembly Hall, and the local market. There are numerous art galleries, souvenir and tailor shops where you can even purchase some express made-to-order clothes!\r\nMEALS INCLUDED: Breakfast'),
