(2867, 146, '_single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_6_short_headline', 'field_5de87cb1618fa'),
(2868, 146, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_6_description', 'By now you’ll be so in love with this stunning country that you’ll just want to lie back and soak it all up. So today you have a free day to do as much, or as little, as you please. It’s your free day and you can get out and about to explore this beautiful town, or lounge around the pool at this fabulous hotel.\r\nMEALS INCLUDED: Breakfast'),
