(2880, 146, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_7_description', 'This morning you’ll have a few more free hours to catch up on last-minute shopping, or enjoy the last few hours at this lovely resort. We’ll check-out of our hotel at noon to head to the airport where we’ll take a flight north to Hanoi - Vietnam’s most charming city. On arrival we’ll be greeted by our driver who will transfer us in to the heart of the city to our next hotel.\r\nMEALS INCLUDED: Breakfast'),
