(2892, 146, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_8_description', 'Welcome to Hanoi! After breakfast, we’ll visit the top highlights during our excellent walking tour around this bustling city. A real kaleidoscope of colours, cultures, the old and the new, Hanoi is truly a fascinating city with so much to see and so much to do.\r\nIn the afternoon, a visit to the Museum of Ethnology where the artifacts of 54 minority groups in Vietnam are exhibited. We’ll then return to the Old Quarter of Hanoi for a walking tour around the Old Streets which were named after the specific goods once offered for sale at these places. Stop at Hoan Kiem Lake to learn about the legend of the lake and a visit to the Ngoc Son Temple.\r\nMEALS INCLUDED: Breakfast'),
