(2915, 146, '_single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_10_short_headline', 'field_5de87cdd61912'),
(2916, 146, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_10_description', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">An incredible day today as we depart our hotel in the morning and head to the Got Harbour for our cruise! </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">On arrival on the ‘junk’, we’ll be served with a welcome drink and a towel, followed by our cruise briefing before checking into our cabins. After setting sail it’s time to enjoy a stunning lunch as we take in the beauty of hundreds of karst islands on our way passing Halong Bay to Lan Ha Bay. </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In the mid-afternoon, we’ll visit the Light and Dark Water Cave, where you can choose to either join the kayaking or board bamboo boat rowed by the local people. Once back aboard the boat, you have the chance to join in a cooking demonstration and learn more about the fabulous Vietnamese cuisine.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tonight you can dine on board as the sunsets and relax at the bar, enjoy the views from the upper deck or even try your hand at karaoke!</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\r\n</span><b>MEALS INCLUDED:</b> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Breakfast, lunch, dinner</span>'),
