(2928, 146, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_11_description', 'As you wake to the stunning vistas you have the option to join an excellent Ta-Chi lesson on the deck before you enjoy a light breakfast in the restaurant. We’ll then disembark the boat for a tour of the wild fresh natural scenery of Cat Ba National Park.\r\nIt’s then back on board the boat for lunch as we cruise back to the harbour where our driver will be waiting to whisk us back to our hotel in Hanoi where we’ll arrive at around 3pm, in plenty of time to freshen up before we head out for a final night farewell group dinner.\r\nMEALS INCLUDED: Breakfast, lunch, dinner'),
