(2940, 146, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_12_description', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sadly, it’s all come to an end today, however, the tour wouldn’t be complete without a final morning celebratory breakfast together as a group. The perfect time to swap contact details, hugs, hi-5’s and a final group photo. Your guide will be sticking around for a while to help you with any onward travel plans that you may have or to give you ideas for more activities that you can join here in Vietnam. </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\r\n</span><b>MEALS INCLUDED:</b> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Breakfast</span>'),
