(2969, 145, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_3_description', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It’s often said that if you travel to India without a trip to the “Monument of Love”, you haven’t really visited India! So today we’re paying a trip to the stunning Taj Mahal! </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The Taj Mahal is one of the New Wonders of the World and even more breathtaking in person. This is a perfect opportunity to try out your new saree to really get a feel for India and her culture. </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">After you get all of the pictures your heart desires at the Taj, we’ll stop Sheroes’ Hangout. Sheroes is a restaurant and cafe managed by brave acid attack survivors. Here we will learn about their </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">social activism in aid of women\'s rights over lunch, and a donation will be made to this awesome cause on your behalf. We will then return to Delhi, where you can take your pick for dinner from Delhi’s amazing food scene or just relax with room service.</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\r\n</span><b>MEALS INCLUDED:</b> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Breakfast, Lunch</span>'),
