(2981, 145, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_4_description', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Today we’ll leave the madness of Delhi and take a short 45-minute flight north to Jolly Grant Airport, Dehradun. Upon arrival at the airport, we’ll have the private transfer for the 40-minute picturesque drive to Ananda in the Himalayas.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Upon arrival at the spa, you will have an individual Ayurvedic wellness consultation to tailor-make your wellness program. You will be guided by Ananda’s team of expert Ayurvedic doctors, skilled therapists, nutritionists, yogis, and chefs. All treatments and meals will be specifically designed for you to create a foundation towards reaching your goals. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> </span><b>MEALS INCLUDED:</b> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Breakfast, lunch, dinner</span>'),
