(2993, 145, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_5_description', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Your program will last 4 days and include five nights of accommodation. Each individual’s program will include ongoing progress checks with ani Ayurvedic Physician, and a detailed debrief and lifestyle consultation before departure. You will have access to all of the hydrotherapy facilities: Steam, Sauna, Chill Plunge Pool, and Kneipp Hydrotherapy Foot Bath, as well as an outdoor pool for relaxing and cooling off.  In addition to your individual therapies, each program includes the following group offerings:</span>'),
