(3005, 145, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_6_description', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sadly, all good things must come to an end! Your time at the resort is officially over, so now we will take the short trip to Rishikesh. Here we can explore the bridges, ashrams, and stunning scenery of Rishikesh, or simply unwind in our hotel with a stunning view of the Ganges. If you want more yoga and meditation, that’s offered as well!</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\r\n</span><b>MEALS INCLUDED:</b> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Breakfast, Morning Wake Up signature tea and fresh fruit bowl</span>'),
