(3017, 145, 'single_tour_custom_fields_itineraries_day_7_description', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sadly, today we must leave Rishikesh, a place that we know you will absolutely fall in love with, and head back to where it all began in New Delhi. We can help you arrange any last-minute activities you may want to experience in Rishikesh. Once back in Delhi, we will have our final group dinner together and there’s no better way to celebrate the end of this incredible experience than with Ladies’ Night!!  We know where to find the best deals (and most fun) for ladies that Delhi has to offer.</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\r\n</span><b>MEALS INCLUDED:</b> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Breakfast, dinner</span>'),
