(17, 2, '2019-11-24 10:58:52', '2019-11-24 10:58:52', 'From Hanoi to Phnom Penh, we’ve crafted an adventure that will show you the very best of Vietnam and Cambodia in just under a fortnight.\r\n\r\nAngkor Wat? Check. Admire it as the sun creeps over the ancient complex. Dreams of sailing Halong Bay? Sorted. Kayak its mysterious limestone caves and stay onboard a traditional junk boat. Your adventure will take you to the most iconic sights of Vietnam and Cambodia, always with a touch of the unexpected. This is Flash Pack, after all.', 'Demo 5 days tour to India', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'demo-5-days-tour-to-india__trashed', '', '', '2019-12-12 03:32:15', '2019-12-12 03:32:15', '', 0, 'https://safarihelps.com/demo/wildones/?post_type=tours&#038;p=17', 0, 'tours', '', 0),
