(135, 2, '2019-12-06 04:00:05', '2019-12-06 04:00:05', 'For those intrepid women who need a little extra adventure, need to get their pulse racing but refuse to miss out on experiencing the beaches and the relaxation that Thailand is so famous for.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Travel as a Wild One as we actively explore the incredible country of Thailand and allow us to showcase for you some of the most exciting and enticing aspects of ‘The Land of Smiles’.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Three of the country\'s most popular locations; Bangkok, Chiang Mai and the beautiful island of Koh Samui will deliver for you some wonderful bite-sized chunks of a country that welcomes over 30 million excited explorers annually.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">From the hustle and bustle of the metropolis of Bangkok, we venture north to the mountainous jungles of Chiang Mai where we’ll hang out with some of the country’s endangered elephants. From there we fly south to the stunningly beautiful island of Koh Samui, where we’ll spend time exploring and relaxing on golden beaches and in the crystal clear ocean.</span>\r\n\r\n<b>SAFETY</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">As with every tour, we operate your safety and comfort are the pillars on which Wild Ones stands. It must be remembered, however, that travelling in any country isn’t without a certain element of risk. Whilst our expert team of guides will move heaven and earth to ensure that the only thing you need to worry about is whether to sunbathe by the pool or on the beach or should I have a cocktail or a glass of wine! </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">For more our safety policies and informative links please click this link -</span><b><i> SAFE TRAVELS</i></b>', 'Thailand Adventure', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'thailand-adventure', '', '', '2019-12-21 07:08:10', '2019-12-21 07:08:10', '', 0, 'https://safarihelps.com/demo/wildones/?post_type=tours&#038;p=135', 0, 'tours', '', 0),
