(467, 2, '2019-12-21 07:14:27', '2019-12-21 07:14:27', 'Discover exactly why Vietnam is the fastest-growing destination for travellers on our expertly curated journey of discovery. From Saigon to Hanoi we’ll showcase for you how this incredible country changes from one city to the next.\n\n<b>SAFETY</b>\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">As with every tour, we operate your safety and comfort are the pillars on which Wild Ones stands. It must be remembered, however, that travelling in any country isn’t without a certain element of risk. Whilst our expert team of guides will move heaven and earth to ensure that the only thing you need to worry about is whether to sunbathe by the pool or on the beach or should I have a cocktail or a glass of wine!</span>\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">For more our safety policies and informative links please click this link -</span><b><i> SAFE TRAVELS</i></b>', 'Vietnam Discovery', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '146-autosave-v1', '', '', '2019-12-21 07:14:27', '2019-12-21 07:14:27', '', 146, 'https://safarihelps.com/demo/wildones/146-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
